title: Watch: Jia Is A Tough Girl With A Soft Side In “Who’s That Girl” MV
text:
Shares 444 Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
Jia (also promoting as Meng Jia) is officially back with her new Chinese single, “Who’s That Girl”! 
As seen in a previously released teaser for the track, the former miss A member is a true fashion chameleon, changing outfits and even hair colors as she sings an introspective rap ballad about trying to better understand herself. The track highlights her versatility as a performer that can easily deliver both edgy and sweet vocals. 
“Who’s That Girl” is the singer’s second single as a solo artist. She made her official Chinese debut back in November with the electro-trap track, “Drip.” 
Check out the full music video below!
